> end rears its ugly head!  It seems that the mechanic has discovered that
> the left rear torsion bar bushings are worn slap out!  I've verified this
> because you can move the entire spring plate front to back (fif) about an
> inch.  Would this looseness cause the rear end to take on a mind of its own
> and cause the back end to sway?  it seems that when driving, the truck
> seems to be steering itself from the rear sometimes (which is
